00:42:09.730 --> 00:42:10.840 align:middle line:90%
How?

00:42:10.840 --> 00:42:12.670 align:middle line:90%
By beauty.

00:42:12.670 --> 00:42:16.120 align:middle line:84%
Plato's banquet on
love talked about how

00:42:16.120 --> 00:42:19.820 align:middle line:84%
to reach the highest
stages of love.

00:42:19.820 --> 00:42:21.740 align:middle line:90%
The same thing goes with beauty.

00:42:21.740 --> 00:42:26.330 align:middle line:84%
Once we begin to
understand-- why can't I

00:42:26.330 --> 00:42:29.660 align:middle line:84%
take that feeling
that I had looking

00:42:29.660 --> 00:42:33.410 align:middle line:84%
at that beautiful picture,
and why not understand

00:42:33.410 --> 00:42:38.050 align:middle line:84%
that I'm living in this
beautiful world with access

00:42:38.050 --> 00:42:40.190 align:middle line:90%
to all of this?

00:42:40.190 --> 00:42:45.020 align:middle line:84%
Understand that we do
have beauty all around us,

00:42:45.020 --> 00:42:47.210 align:middle line:90%
and we will become beautiful.

00:42:47.210 --> 00:42:49.040 align:middle line:84%
We're back to my
opening statement

00:42:49.040 --> 00:42:51.260 align:middle line:90%
about environment is everything.

00:42:51.260 --> 00:42:53.450 align:middle line:90%
