00:42:53.450 --> 00:42:56.390 align:middle line:84%
The castle was a
perfect environment.

00:42:56.390 --> 00:43:00.800 align:middle line:84%
What makes the supreme
healers on the planet?

00:43:00.800 --> 00:43:03.185 align:middle line:84%
Is it just their
energy, or is it

00:43:03.185 --> 00:43:07.190 align:middle line:84%
that they create an environment
where you and I believe

00:43:07.190 --> 00:43:09.020 align:middle line:90%
