00:43:09.020 --> 00:43:11.530 align:middle line:84%
REGINA MEREDITH: Right,
right, it supports them.

00:43:11.530 --> 00:43:15.660 align:middle line:84%
And this is something that
you have held as a core

00:43:15.660 --> 00:43:17.030 align:middle line:90%
to your being your whole life.

00:43:17.030 --> 00:43:17.540 align:middle line:90%
STEVEN ROSS: Yes.

